WEBVTT

00:01:22.680 --> 00:01:23.120
President Lu,

00:01:24.599 --> 00:01:25.400
you're

00:01:27.920 --> 00:01:28.719
turning on me.

00:01:31.079 --> 00:01:31.799
Jiao Shiheng.

00:01:31.799 --> 00:01:32.599
Hey.

00:01:32.799 --> 00:01:34.280
Leng Qingqiu is my fiancée.

00:01:34.760 --> 00:01:36.120
How dare you flirt with her?

00:01:36.280 --> 00:01:37.079
President Lu,

00:01:37.280 --> 00:01:37.840
it's a misunderstanding.

00:01:37.840 --> 00:01:38.560
A misunderstanding.

00:01:38.799 --> 00:01:39.400
It's all a misunderstanding.

00:01:39.400 --> 00:01:40.079
We're just talking business.

00:01:40.079 --> 00:01:40.560
Beat him

00:01:40.560 --> 00:01:41.159
up!

00:01:41.159 --> 00:01:41.560
Yes.

00:01:41.560 --> 00:01:42.159
President Lu,

00:01:42.159 --> 00:01:43.159
we're talking business, President Lu!

00:01:43.519 --> 00:01:44.280
Cut the crap.

00:01:44.280 --> 00:01:44.599
President Lu!

00:01:44.599 --> 00:01:45.319
Young Master,

00:01:45.319 --> 00:01:46.120
how should I beat him?

00:01:47.480 --> 00:01:48.079
You

00:01:48.079 --> 00:01:48.920
hit him first.

00:01:49.079 --> 00:01:49.959
Let me watch

00:01:50.120 --> 00:01:50.920
and get a feel for it.

00:01:51.480 --> 00:01:51.719
Yes.

00:01:51.719 --> 00:01:52.120
Don't hit the head!

00:01:52.120 --> 00:01:52.920
Don't hit the head!

00:01:56.560 --> 00:01:57.359
Stop messing around.

00:01:57.760 --> 00:01:58.560
Lu Chengwen!

00:01:59.599 --> 00:02:01.000
When I'm doing things,

00:02:01.400 --> 00:02:02.879
don't interrupt my train of thought.

00:02:03.560 --> 00:02:04.359
Continue.

00:02:08.360 --> 00:02:09.159
Alright,

00:02:09.479 --> 00:02:10.680
I just won't sign it.

00:02:11.120 --> 00:02:12.719
I want to talk to you alone.

00:02:13.080 --> 00:02:13.879
Zhao Gang,

00:02:15.919 --> 00:02:16.719
clear the room.

00:02:17.479 --> 00:02:18.319
President Leng.

00:02:19.280 --> 00:02:20.280
Take this thing away

00:02:20.400 --> 00:02:21.199
and burn it.

00:02:27.159 --> 00:02:28.199
Put your legs down.

00:02:29.719 --> 00:02:31.080
I'm used to being like this.

00:02:32.199 --> 00:02:33.000
One.

00:02:35.919 --> 00:02:37.360
I can't find Gu Zhantian.

00:02:37.520 --> 00:02:38.639
Then I can only

00:02:38.639 --> 00:02:39.560
go beg Xu Xuejiao.

00:02:39.919 --> 00:02:41.400
I'll just have to try a desperate measure.

00:02:42.599 --> 00:02:43.680
I have things to do,

00:02:43.719 --> 00:02:44.479
I'll leave first.

00:02:46.120 --> 00:02:47.080
Stop pretending.

00:02:53.800 --> 00:02:55.719
I know you have feelings for me.

00:02:56.319 --> 00:02:58.280
About what your mom said regarding our marriage,

00:02:58.479 --> 00:02:59.360
I have no objections.

00:02:59.719 --> 00:03:00.680
No way.

00:03:01.080 --> 00:03:02.319
Are you clinging to me now?

00:03:10.159 --> 00:03:10.919
I don't believe I

00:03:10.919 --> 00:03:12.280
can't scare you away.

00:03:22.479 --> 00:03:23.400
What are you doing?

00:03:27.599 --> 00:03:28.280
Back then,

00:03:28.280 --> 00:03:29.719
when I begged you,

00:03:29.719 --> 00:03:30.960
you ignored me.

00:03:31.520 --> 00:03:33.000
Now that I'm annoyed,

00:03:34.080 --> 00:03:35.560
you're getting all excited.

00:03:36.120 --> 00:03:36.919
Fine.

00:03:37.800 --> 00:03:39.759
Then I'll let you see

00:03:39.919 --> 00:03:41.759
who you're messing with.

00:03:42.360 --> 00:03:43.400
Don't mess around.

00:03:44.599 --> 00:03:45.400
Mess around?

00:03:45.719 --> 00:03:46.719
Villains can

00:03:46.719 --> 00:03:47.960
do whatever they want.

00:04:03.560 --> 00:04:04.960
Why are you closing your eyes?

00:04:05.280 --> 00:04:06.319
Giving up resistance?

00:04:06.759 --> 00:04:08.479
Doesn't that put me in a tough spot?

00:04:16.879 --> 00:04:18.680
So he's just pretending to be a jerk with me.

00:04:19.120 --> 00:04:19.920
Got it.

00:04:24.160 --> 00:04:25.000
What's going on?

00:04:25.360 --> 00:04:27.120
Weren't you looking very nervous just now?

00:04:27.199 --> 00:04:27.959
Why are you suddenly

00:04:27.959 --> 00:04:28.920
so fearless?

00:04:35.279 --> 00:04:36.079
You...

00:04:37.079 --> 00:04:37.920
Boring.

00:04:38.120 --> 00:04:38.720
Well,

00:04:38.720 --> 00:04:39.680
I like

00:04:39.680 --> 00:04:41.000
girls who take the initiative.

00:04:41.959 --> 00:04:42.519
You,

00:04:42.519 --> 00:04:43.600
come kiss me.

00:04:45.279 --> 00:04:46.079
What?

00:04:46.319 --> 00:04:47.120
Scared?

00:04:49.800 --> 00:04:51.519
If you're scared, don't come looking for me.

00:04:53.160 --> 00:04:53.920
You...

00:05:03.920 --> 00:05:05.319
Wh-what are you doing?

00:05:23.759 --> 00:05:25.120
I let you kiss me earlier, but you didn't.

00:05:25.600 --> 00:05:26.519
Now,

00:05:26.519 --> 00:05:27.720
it's too late.

00:05:28.000 --> 00:05:28.920
I

00:05:28.920 --> 00:05:29.920
lost interest.

00:05:30.000 --> 00:05:30.879
I've got things to do.

00:05:30.879 --> 00:05:31.680
I'm off.

00:05:32.279 --> 00:05:33.079
Young Master Lu,

00:05:33.519 --> 00:05:35.199
if you ever want a kiss,

00:05:35.279 --> 00:05:36.360
remember to come find me.

00:05:48.000 --> 00:05:48.920
I'm sure of it.

00:05:49.199 --> 00:05:51.519
Leng Qingqiu definitely knows what I'm thinking.

00:05:51.959 --> 00:05:54.319
But why did she later...

00:05:54.800 --> 00:05:56.120
It was so close!

00:05:56.519 --> 00:05:58.319
Is Leng Qingqiu out of her mind today?

00:05:58.920 --> 00:06:00.120
This is killing me.

00:06:05.000 --> 00:06:05.720
Young Master.

00:06:05.720 --> 00:06:06.439
Just now...

00:06:06.439 --> 00:06:07.800
Did you kiss Miss Leng?

00:06:09.319 --> 00:06:10.120
No, I didn't.

00:06:10.120 --> 00:06:11.079
Nothing happened between us.

00:06:11.079 --> 00:06:12.480
Don't you dare talk nonsense to others.

00:06:12.600 --> 00:06:13.360
Okay, okay, okay.

00:06:13.360 --> 00:06:14.360
Go bring the car around.

00:06:14.360 --> 00:06:15.519
I'm going to find Xu Xuejiao.

00:06:15.519 --> 00:06:15.680
Yes.

00:06:15.680 --> 00:06:16.480
Okay.

00:06:19.920 --> 00:06:20.800
Young Master Lu.

00:06:20.959 --> 00:06:23.279
Someone reported that you committed public assault again.

00:06:23.279 --> 00:06:24.519
Come with us.

00:06:28.920 --> 00:06:29.519
Officer.

00:06:29.600 --> 00:06:30.959
Can you let me make a phone call first?

00:06:30.959 --> 00:06:31.920
It's a matter of life and death.

00:06:32.160 --> 00:06:32.959
Make it right here.

00:06:32.959 --> 00:06:33.920
Don't try any tricks with me.

00:06:34.120 --> 00:06:34.519
Okay.

00:06:34.519 --> 00:06:35.319
Thank you.

00:06:38.399 --> 00:06:39.279
Sister Xuejiao.

00:06:39.720 --> 00:06:40.759
Brother Chengwen.

00:06:41.120 --> 00:06:42.079
What's up?

00:06:42.279 --> 00:06:44.120
Jiang Shihan's mother...

00:06:44.120 --> 00:06:45.480
Is critically ill right now.

00:06:45.480 --> 00:06:46.279
She had an attack.

00:06:46.360 --> 00:06:47.519
Her condition is very dangerous.

00:06:47.680 --> 00:06:49.160
Can you save her?

00:06:49.519 --> 00:06:50.279
Oh.

00:06:50.600 --> 00:06:51.399
No.

00:06:51.759 --> 00:06:52.959
I don't even know her well.

00:06:53.279 --> 00:06:54.199
Besides...

00:06:54.279 --> 00:06:56.120
I don't just treat anyone.

00:06:56.399 --> 00:06:58.279
Please just help her mother.

00:06:58.279 --> 00:06:58.800
Fine.

00:06:58.800 --> 00:07:00.120
Consider it a favor I owe you.

00:07:01.759 --> 00:07:03.399
Are you begging me?

00:07:04.560 --> 00:07:05.319
Yes.

00:07:05.319 --> 00:07:06.480
I'm begging you.

00:07:07.480 --> 00:07:08.279
Grandma.

00:07:08.519 --> 00:07:09.319
Great-grandma.

00:07:09.399 --> 00:07:10.360
As long as you're willing to help her...

00:07:10.360 --> 00:07:11.920
I'll do anything for you.

00:07:13.399 --> 00:07:15.160
I don't want to be your great-grandma.

00:07:16.079 --> 00:07:17.000
Besides...

00:07:17.160 --> 00:07:18.800
If you're begging, act like it.

00:07:19.000 --> 00:07:19.600
How about this.

00:07:19.600 --> 00:07:20.639
You transfer the pharmaceutical factory's...

00:07:20.639 --> 00:07:22.399
All of its shares to me.

00:07:22.519 --> 00:07:23.800
Without asking for a single cent.

00:07:24.160 --> 00:07:25.519
Promise me, and I'll help you.

00:07:25.519 --> 00:07:26.160
How about it?

00:07:26.160 --> 00:07:26.920
Okay.

00:07:26.920 --> 00:07:27.680
I promise you.

00:07:28.319 --> 00:07:29.360
Really?

00:07:29.759 --> 00:07:31.279
The factory is worth thirty billion.

00:07:31.519 --> 00:07:33.720
The Lu family's share is over eighteen billion.

00:07:35.319 --> 00:07:37.000
For a mere secretary...

00:07:37.600 --> 00:07:39.120
You're willing to give it up to me?

00:07:39.120 --> 00:07:39.759
I...

00:07:39.759 --> 00:07:40.560
No...

00:07:45.160 --> 00:07:45.720
Because I...

00:07:45.720 --> 00:07:46.560
Like her.

00:07:47.079 --> 00:07:47.879
I love her.

00:07:48.120 --> 00:07:49.120
I want to marry her and take her home.

00:07:49.120 --> 00:07:49.920
To be my wife.

00:07:49.920 --> 00:07:50.680
Is that enough?

00:07:51.360 --> 00:07:52.160
You...

00:07:52.319 --> 00:07:53.120
I...

00:07:53.680 --> 00:07:54.800
I still don't believe it.

00:07:55.120 --> 00:07:55.680
Unless...

00:07:55.680 --> 00:07:57.279
Unless you come over and sign the contract with me right now.

00:07:57.279 --> 00:07:57.560
Wait.

00:07:57.560 --> 00:07:58.199
Lady.

00:07:58.279 --> 00:07:59.519
I'm about to go to the police station.

00:07:59.519 --> 00:08:00.720
How can I sign a contract with you?

00:08:00.800 --> 00:08:02.199
Wait for me to get out, and I'll sign it for you.

00:08:02.199 --> 00:08:03.879
I'll give you all the factory shares then.

00:08:03.879 --> 00:08:04.800
Hurry up and save her now.

00:08:04.800 --> 00:08:05.519
Save her!

00:08:05.680 --> 00:08:06.319
Lu Chengwen.

00:08:06.319 --> 00:08:07.399
How dare you yell at me!

00:08:07.600 --> 00:08:08.319
Fine.

00:08:08.319 --> 00:08:09.800
You want me to save her, right?

00:08:09.800 --> 00:08:10.600
Fine.

00:08:10.720 --> 00:08:11.720
Just you wait.

00:08:16.279 --> 00:08:17.800
Are you going to save her or not?

00:08:18.920 --> 00:08:20.279
I didn't expect Young Master Lu...

00:08:20.279 --> 00:08:21.480
To actually be saving someone.

00:08:21.600 --> 00:08:22.800
Come with us.

00:08:24.199 --> 00:08:25.399
He's changed, he's really changed.

00:08:25.399 --> 00:08:25.720
Let's go.

00:08:25.720 --> 00:08:26.519
Let's go.

00:08:31.680 --> 00:08:32.720
Don't worry.

00:08:33.120 --> 00:08:34.720
Since I promised to do the surgery for your mom,

00:08:34.720 --> 00:08:35.679
I won't go back on my word.

00:08:36.279 --> 00:08:37.360
Thank you, Dr. Xu.

00:08:38.919 --> 00:08:39.799
President Lu just

00:08:39.799 --> 00:08:40.480
said

00:08:40.480 --> 00:08:42.120
he's going to jail.

00:08:42.159 --> 00:08:43.200
I'll go bail him out.

00:08:43.919 --> 00:08:44.919
That jerk.

00:08:45.000 --> 00:08:46.080
How dare he yell at me.

00:08:48.559 --> 00:08:49.519
President Lu probably

00:08:49.519 --> 00:08:50.600
doesn't know yet

00:08:50.600 --> 00:08:52.120
that Dr. Xu has already

00:08:52.120 --> 00:08:53.879
helped stabilize my mom's condition.

00:08:55.120 --> 00:08:56.279
To help me,

00:08:56.679 --> 00:08:58.320
he actually gave the pharmaceutical factory shares

00:08:58.320 --> 00:08:59.679
all to Dr. Xu.

00:09:00.120 --> 00:09:01.720
He also said

00:09:01.720 --> 00:09:03.200
he likes me.

00:09:07.200 --> 00:09:08.200
The vice president next to you

00:09:08.200 --> 00:09:09.720
was bribed and you didn't even know.

00:09:10.080 --> 00:09:11.799
How do you manage this company?

00:09:12.279 --> 00:09:14.480
If it weren't for Lu Chengwen this time,

00:09:14.799 --> 00:09:16.320
our Leng family would be finished.

00:09:16.759 --> 00:09:17.639
However,

00:09:17.639 --> 00:09:18.960
it exactly shows

00:09:19.279 --> 00:09:21.320
that this kid really cares about you.

00:09:21.799 --> 00:09:22.919
About the engagement,

00:09:22.919 --> 00:09:24.399
how are your discussions going?

00:09:25.320 --> 00:09:26.080
Dad,

00:09:26.080 --> 00:09:27.799
don't mention this to me again.

00:09:28.120 --> 00:09:29.080
What did you say?

00:09:29.759 --> 00:09:31.000
Your marriage

00:09:31.000 --> 00:09:32.919
concerns the survival of the enterprise

00:09:33.120 --> 00:09:34.200
and the rise and fall of the family.

00:09:34.320 --> 00:09:35.480
This principle,

00:09:35.480 --> 00:09:36.879
do you still not understand it?

00:09:37.159 --> 00:09:37.919
This time,

00:09:37.919 --> 00:09:39.200
it's Lu Chengwen who disagreed.

00:09:39.559 --> 00:09:41.360
Can't you take the initiative?

00:09:41.919 --> 00:09:44.399
You put on a cold, icy face all day.

00:09:44.480 --> 00:09:45.679
Who would like that?

00:09:46.000 --> 00:09:47.679
I don't care what method you use,

00:09:47.919 --> 00:09:48.879
next month,

00:09:48.879 --> 00:09:49.879
you must get engaged.

00:09:50.000 --> 00:09:51.039
Otherwise,

00:09:51.039 --> 00:09:52.200
I'll convene the board of directors

00:09:52.279 --> 00:09:53.919
and remove you from the CEO position.

00:10:00.879 --> 00:10:01.559
President Leng,

00:10:01.559 --> 00:10:03.080
President Lu was taken away by the police.

00:10:03.320 --> 00:10:05.320
I heard President Jiao Shiheng called the police.

00:10:05.679 --> 00:10:06.519
Get the car ready immediately.

00:10:06.519 --> 00:10:07.360
We're going to the police station.

00:10:07.360 --> 00:10:08.159
Yes.

00:10:10.480 --> 00:10:10.960
You may leave.

00:10:10.960 --> 00:10:11.720
Lu Chengwen,

00:10:11.720 --> 00:10:13.320
Jiao Shiheng has signed the settlement agreement.

00:10:13.320 --> 00:10:14.279
Be careful next time.

00:10:16.960 --> 00:10:17.879
Why is it her?

00:10:18.320 --> 00:10:19.480
I thought Xu Xuejiao

00:10:19.480 --> 00:10:20.519
wanted to quickly sign the contract with me

00:10:20.519 --> 00:10:21.320
so she bailed me out.

00:10:24.200 --> 00:10:25.000
What?

00:10:25.279 --> 00:10:26.559
Are you disappointed to see me?

00:10:27.679 --> 00:10:28.480
No,

00:10:28.480 --> 00:10:29.480
how could I be?

00:10:30.480 --> 00:10:31.159
Sorry to trouble you,

00:10:31.159 --> 00:10:31.919
Qingqiu.

00:10:31.919 --> 00:10:32.679
It's no trouble.

00:10:33.679 --> 00:10:34.480
Let's go.

00:10:35.919 --> 00:10:36.720
Lu Chengwen.

00:10:38.480 --> 00:10:40.360
Can't you take the initiative?

00:10:40.480 --> 00:10:42.919
You put on a cold, icy face all day.

00:10:42.919 --> 00:10:44.120
Who would like that?

00:10:44.279 --> 00:10:45.759
I don't care what method you use,

00:10:46.000 --> 00:10:46.879
next month,

00:10:46.879 --> 00:10:47.919
you must get engaged.

00:10:53.559 --> 00:10:54.639
I actually

00:10:54.639 --> 00:10:56.080
really regret that

00:10:56.080 --> 00:10:57.960
I didn't cherish your feelings for me before.

00:11:00.600 --> 00:11:01.480
Can we

00:11:01.480 --> 00:11:03.080
just start over?